      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Avian shields:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Only avians who prefer ground combat use a shield bound to their wings to defend themselves against attacks.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The AC bonus guaranteed by wingshield applies only while the avian wearing is not in flight.</span></p>",
